	‚Ä¢	proof-of-work
	‚Ä¢	difficulty adjustment
	‚Ä¢	hashrate dominance
	‚Ä¢	energy efficiency curves
These are not tools; they are institutional makeup.
3.2 The Brevity Flop
A simple, elegant mining setup is fatal.
A hypothetical return to ‚Äúone CPU, one vote‚Äù would be rejected for:
	‚Ä¢	lacking a œá-graded ASIC lattice
	‚Ä¢	failing to reference industrial-scale immersion cooling
	‚Ä¢	insufficient energy density
	‚Ä¢	unacceptable accessibility
The system eliminates the individual because they can be included too easily.

4. The Corporate Feedback Loop: Training Machines to Prefer Scale
Here lies the final crisis: the protocol, born of cypherpunk idealism, now trains its participants in a terrible lesson:
Wasteful = authoritative.
It observes that:
	‚Ä¢	the largest farms are the most secure
	‚Ä¢	the highest burn appears the most committed
	‚Ä¢	confidence correlates with kilowatt-hours
